query: SELECT si.id, si.sku, si.sourceStore, SUBSTRING(si.s3Url, 1, 150) as s3Url_short, oi.orderId FROM scrapedImages si JOIN orderItems oi ON si.orderItemId = oi.id WHERE oi.orderId IN (270018, 270019) ORDER BY si.id DESC LIMIT 10
